text:
BREAKING. The DOH records 16 “fresh” and 846 “late” coronavirus cases on Sunday, May 31. Total cases now at 18,086.

The DOH also reports 7 new deaths, raising the death toll to 957, while 101 new patients recovered from the virus, bringing the total recoveries to 3,909. https://t.co/eTE7C5ibHd
